data.description: Ready to move in!! Wonderful & well maintained 3 bdrm home tucked away in the desirable Pinewood Colony. NO HOA! Great Cul De Sac Location. Relaxing covered front porch. Updates throughout including LVT flooring, fresh paint, all new carpet! Open Kitchen/eat in space w/ SS appliances. Spacious Liv rm. Step out back to a lg deck & lg backyd for family cookouts & entertaining. Fam Rm w/ brick hearth frpl. Lg primary suite. 1st fl laundry. Finished Rec area & utility/storage space. Conveniently located to all the awesome Westerville amenities we love. Near highway access, parks, shopping center, St Ann Hospital, airport & much more! See HOME IMPROVEMENT LIST!
